rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0001
rows.name: Okay, time to cross the desert.

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0002
rows.name:
Has everyone taken their
Desert-Crossing Medicine?

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0006
rows.name:
We took it together after we woke up
this morning! We're good!

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0007
rows.name:
Alright, let's head out.
Once we're in the Dannagh Desert, we'll
be able to see the capital right away.

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0008
rows.name: Good, so we won't get lost.

rows.label: fev11_530_175_msg0009
rows.name:
Right. We don't have time to waste
getting lost. We need to inform the King
about Metsu's target ASAP.
